    <td colspan="4" valign="top">
       <p><span class="mg">CCP4mg</span>
is the quick and easy way to create beautiful publication quality
images and movies. It is also the easy way to superpose and analyse
structures. See the <a class="application" href="functionality.html">Functionality</a> page for details.</p>
       
       <p>The program runs 'out of the box' on Linux, MacOSX and Windows platforms.</p>
       <table class="highlight">
        <tr><td > 
